# --- DataSets ---------------------------
# --- Declare el URI para el conjunto de datos, especifique dónde se define su estructura,
# --- y cuál es su etiqueta.
<https://example.org/id/datacube/casesCovid>   rdf:type qb:DataSet ;   
 qb:structure <https://example.org/id/dsd/casesCovid> ;   
 rdfs:label "cases Covid dataset"@en ;
.
# --- Data Structure Definition (DSD) ---------------------------
# --- Declare el URI para la definición de estructura de datos y luego especifique 
# --- la unidad de medida, que se especificará como 
# --- sdmx-attribute: unitMeasure en las observaciones;
# --- las dimensiones del cubo: refArea, refPeriod
# --- la variable medida: número;
# --- y la etiqueta para el DSD.

<https://example.org/id/dsd/casesCovid> rdf:type qb:DataStructureDefinition ;
qb:component [rdf:type qb:ComponentSpecification ;
qb:attribute sdmx-attribute:unitMeasure;] ; 
qb:component [rdf:type qb:ComponentSpecification ;  	 
qb:dimension sdmx-dimension:refPeriod ; ] ;
qb:component [rdf:type qb:ComponentSpecification ;  	 
qb:dimension <https://example.org/ns/casesCovid#typecases> ; ] ;
qb:component [rdf:type qb:ComponentSpecification ;  	 
qb:dimension <https://example.org/ns/casesCovid#Country> ; ] ;
qb:component [rdf:type qb:ComponentSpecification ;  	 
qb:measure <https://example.org/ns/casesCovid#numberofcases> ; ] ;
rdfs:label "dsd for datacube casesCovid"@en ;
.
# --- Propiedades de dimensión ---------------------------
<https://example.org/ns/casesCovid#Country> rdf:type qb:CodedProperty ;   
 rdf:type qb:DimensionProperty ;
 qb:codeList <https://example.org/id/conceptscheme/Region> ;      
 rdfs:label "Regions of the Equator"@en ;   
 rdfs:range skos:Concept ;
.
<https://example.org/ns/casesCovid#typecases>   rdf:type qb:CodedProperty ;   
 rdf:type qb:DimensionProperty ;
 qb:codeList <https://example.org/id/conceptscheme/typecases> ;      
 rdfs:label "type of cases"@en ;   
 rdfs:range skos:Concept ;
.
  # --- Propiedades de medida ---------------------------
<https://example.org/ns/casesCovid#numberofcases>   rdf:type qb:MeasureProperty ;   
 rdfs:label "number of cases for Covid"@en ; 
rdfs:subPropertyOf sdmx-measure:obsValue;  
 rdfs:range xsd:integer ;
.
# --- ConceptScheme (Vocabulario controlado) para tipos de casos ------
<https://example.org/id/conceptscheme/typecases>   rdf:type skos:ConceptScheme ;   
 rdfs:label "types of cases"@en;   
 skos:hasTopConcept <https://example.org/id/concept/allcases> ;
.
<https://example.org/id/concept/allcases>   rdf:type skos:Concept ;   
 rdfs:label "all types cases"@en ;   
 skos:inScheme <https://example.org/id/conceptscheme/typecases> ;   
 skos:narrower <https://example.org/id/concept/confirmedCanton> ;
  skos:narrower <https://example.org/id/concept/confirmedProvince> ;
 skos:narrower <https://example.org/id/concept/ConfirmedRegion> ;   
 skos:narrower <https://example.org/id/concept/deceasedProvince> ; 
.
<https://example.org/id/concept/confirmedCanton>  rdf:type skos:Concept ;   
 rdfs:label "confirmed of covid-19 for Canton"@en ;   
 skos:inScheme <https://example.org/id/conceptscheme/typecases> ;
 skos:broader <https://example.org/id/concept/allcases> ;
 .
<https://example.org/id/concept/confirmedProvince>   rdf:type skos:Concept ;   
 rdfs:label "confirmed of covid-19 for Province"@en ;   
 skos:inScheme <https://example.org/id/conceptscheme/typecases> ;
 skos:broader <https://example.org/id/concept/allcases> ;
.
<https://example.org/id/concept/confirmedRegion>   rdf:type skos:Concept ;   
 rdfs:label "confirmed of covid-19 for Region"@en ;   
 skos:inScheme <https://example.org/id/conceptscheme/typecases> ;
 skos:broader <https://example.org/id/concept/allcases> ;
.
<https://example.org/id/concept/deceasedProvince>   rdf:type skos:Concept ;   
 rdfs:label "deceased the covid-19 for Province"@en ;   
 skos:inScheme <https://example.org/id/conceptscheme/typecases> ;
 skos:broader <https://example.org/id/concept/allcases> ;.
